  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Euclid
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Mapping the expansion of the Universe to better understand dark energy and matter. Launching in 2022 for a 6-year mission. </p>

  </div>
</div>

